      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! Up for grabs is my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one, and honestly, she looks like she just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been garage-kept, hand-washed every Sunday, and drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019m only parting with it to make room for a new project, but I\u2019m looking for a neighbor who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come by, grab a coffee, and let's get you behind the wheel of this pristine machine!",
