      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute specimen of Bavarian engineering. This chassis has been meticulously curated with a focus on mechanical longevity and tactile precision. The S54 powerplant exhibits razor-sharp throttle response, having undergone a comprehensive VANOS overhaul with cryo-treated hubs and Beisan seals. Subframe reinforcement\u2014a critical preventative measure\u2014was executed with structural plates and solid bushings to eliminate any deflection under high-load cornering. We\u2019ve verified the rod bearing clearances via regular Blackstone oil analysis, ensuring the bottom end remains bulletproof. Suspended on a perfectly dampened Bilstein coilover setup, the kinematics are dialed for maximum feedback without sacrificing compliance. The limited-slip differential lockup is immediate, and the shifting action is crisp with zero synchro hesitation. This isn't just a car; it's a high-fidelity driving tool maintained to a standard that exceeds factory specifications. Turn-key and ready for the most discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
